 Remember to change your email password in any email apps  including Outlook  that you use on your computer  tablet  or mobile phone to match your new Office 365 password  How do alumni connect to email  To access your email go to this location  http vmiconnect vmi edu or http outlook com mail vmi edu  My password is not working  If you are a cadet and you are unable to use the reset password option on the Office 365 site  take your photo ID to the Barracks Help Desk and your password can be reset  If you are an alumni or a cadet who is off Post  you will need to email help vmi edu for instructions  Will my email address change  No  your email address will not change  Will my email account be deleted when I graduate or leave VMI  No  One of the advantages of this email system is a  lifetime  VMI account  Upon graduation or leaving the Institute you will keep your VMI email account for life  What browsers can I use to access my email account  Most web browsers support the Outlook Web application that you use to access your email  If you use a browser that doesn t support the full feature set  Outlook Web App will open in a light version  For further details  visit Microsoft s Outlook Web App Supported Browsers knowledge base entry  Can I keep track of other email accounts  such as Gmail  from within my email account  Yes  please see Microsoft s instructions on how to keep track of email from other accounts by connecting to them from your Outlook Web App account  You can connect up to five other accounts  such as Hotmail  Gmail  and Yahoo  Mail accounts  This lets you send  receive  and read mail from all the accounts in one place    Can I access my email with a desktop client such as Outlook  Yes  you can access your account with different email clients  such as Outlook Mac Mail  etc  To find your desktop client IMAP or POP  port and SSL settings  sign in to your VMIconnect account and click the   For Help  then click About  Note  If you don t know whether to use IMAP4 or POP3  consider IMAP4 because it supports more features and always keeps a local copy of the message on the server after you retrieve a copy to your local computer  How can I get more information on using Outlook Web App to access my email account  Get help with Outlook Web App when you login to your email account  Can I access my email by mobile phone or other devices  Yes  please see the Outlook Web App mobile phone instructions  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 